@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml
title 分布式锁运行总览时序图

actor Biz as "业务代码"
participant Client as "DistributedLockClient"
participant Core as "Core"
participant Provider as "LockProvider"
database Store as "Redis/ZK/Etcd"

Biz -> Client : execute / tryLock
Client -> Core : 编排锁流程
Core -> Provider : acquire / renew / release / check
Provider -> Store : 底层原子操作
Store --> Provider : 底层结果
Provider --> Core : ProviderStatus / Response
Core --> Client : LockResult / LockHandle
Client --> Biz : result

@enduml
